<b><big><u>Property Description</u></big></b><br><br>
Welcome to Ryan Tower + Monterey Garden these two landmark buildings are located within the heart of San Mateo’s magnificent serene and exclusive Baywood District. Both conveniently located just two blocks from downtown San Mateo. Downtown offers shopping, bistros, grocery stores, fine dining, a 12 screen cinema, 24 Hour Fitness, a new public library, Central Park, and lots of other entertainment. Ryan Tower is a newly renovated dramatic high rise with pet-friendly studios, 1, 2, and 3 bedroom apartment homes, most with dramatic views of the bay or hills. Conveniently located just 2 blocks west of El Camino on Third Avenue, a short distance to Caltrain, as well as minutes to the 101 and 280 Freeways.<br><br>
